== Multiple layouts ==

The feature introduced in XFree86 4.3.0. It allows to concatenate one-group symbol descriptions into the complex, up to 4 groups (hard limit by XKB) layouts.

Currently this feature is supported by
	* [[http://www.xfree.org/releases/rel430.html|XFree86 Release 4.3.0]]
	* [[http://www.xfree.org/releases/rel440.html|XFree86 Release 4.4.0]]
        * [[http://www.xfree.org/releases/rel450.html|XFree86 Release 4.5.0]]
	* [[http://xorg.freedesktop.org/wiki/ReleaseNotes670|X.Org Release 6.7.0]]

More about this feature read [[http://xlibs.freedesktop.org/xkbdesc/xkbconfig.pdf|here in PDF]] or [[http://xlibs.freedesktop.org/xkbdesc/xkbconfig.sxw|here in OOo format]]. 

